{"tid":1988132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全球抵制支國貨大行動！由香港做起！","createTime":"2020-04-25T04:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:16:46.000Z","uid":321893,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e951ece45f534502a2191252fa162d93fd177f9c","tid":1988132,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"想支爆一係等美帝出兵，一係等大陸人民醒覺反共，等得黎都蚊訓。<br />\n趁住武漢肺炎肆虐，全球人類開始對支共產生厭惡感既時候，我地黎發起全球抵制支國貨，打沉支共既經濟，支爆就指日可待，全球人只要知道以下兩點：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 不購買任何支國品牌<br />\n2. 不購買任何 Made in Cina 既產品 - 迫使全球公司在支國撤廠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵制原因：<br />\n1. 支共至今已經殘殺國內外人接近一億<br />\n2. 支共為武漢肺炎的來源國，禍害全球，不但推卸責任，更封鎖資訊，使疫情肆虐。<br />\n3. 支國貨本來就劣質，不值得買。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n行動：<br />\n<br />\n1. 文宣 - 用以上紅字資料造成文宣，要多國語言既文宣，英文、西班牙文、意大利文、正體中文、日文、韓文、等等，越多越好。<br />\n<br />\n2. 發放以上文宣到全世界任何一個角落。<br />\n<br />\n3. 任何可以宣揚以上訊息既方法，例如聯署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得此post有用既請正評及幫手推。唔該。"},{"pid":"91ffb6673e1004e8ac1cbb59c0b59efee061da58","tid":1988132,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"好多年前已經 ABC anywhere but China <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1513229a82941d05aa745fb11c13a05198962881","tid":1988132,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:39:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8983ceec32a2389b3c5df5cfa56676a2311541f","tid":1988132,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:39:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ceda144c2cdf3686e4ae28af69cef792062a070d","tid":1988132,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91ffb6673e1004